text: XHCHAL-FM is a community radio station on 98.9 FM in Chalco de Díaz Covarrubias, State of Mexico. It is known as Contacto FM and owned by the civil association Comunicaciones en Contacto, Cultura y Bienestar Social, A.C. ==History== XHCHAL was approved for its concession on September 6, 2017.IFT: Award of frequency The frequency had been applied for on May 9, 2016. ==References== Category:Radio stations in the State of Mexico Category:Community radio stations in Mexico Category:Former pirate radio stations
